Package: pipnode-zigbee-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Enhances: pipnode-run, pipnode-editor
Description: pipnode Zigbee control/query nodes (headless)
 Out-of-tree plugin for the pipnode visual dataflow environment, adding
 nodes that drive Zigbee devices through a Zigbee2MQTT instance over
 MQTT.
 .
 The module is GTK-free: it links libpipnode-core only and is picked up
 by both the headless runner (pipnode-run) and the editor. Ships the
 PnZigbeeSource, PnZigbeeSwitch and PnZnpPing nodes, their per-node HTML
 help pages, and example worksheets under the editor's "zigbee" category.
